name: WDesignkit
author: POSIMYTH

sections.description:
WDdesignKit is a powerful WordPress plugin that offers a wide range of website templates and custom widgets/blocks for both Elementor and Gutenberg. With a collection of over 100 templates and more than 20 custom widgets/blocks for each page builder, WDdesignKit is designed to enhance your website building experience and provide you with the tools you need to create stunning websites with ease.

Quick Navigation Links
🌐Visit Website | 🎥 Video Tutorials | 📑 Documentations | 🛣️ Roadmap | 👥 Join Community | 🤝 Free Support | ⭐ Premium Support

👑 Exclusive Features of WDesingKit

  • 100+ Elementor Templates: Choose from a wide variety of pre-designed templates for Elementor, allowing you to quickly create professional-looking websites. Whether you need templates for landing pages, blogs, portfolios, or any other type of website, WDdesignKit has got you covered.

  • 20+ Elementor Custom Widgets: Take your Elementor website to the next level with our custom widgets. These widgets are specifically designed to enhance the functionality and design options available in Elementor. From advanced sliders to interactive maps, you can easily incorporate these widgets into your website and create a truly unique online presence.

  • 100+ Gutenberg Templates: If you prefer using the Gutenberg editor, WDdesignKit provides you with an extensive collection of templates that are compatible with Gutenberg. With a wide range of options available, you can effortlessly create visually appealing websites using the native WordPress block editor.

  • 20+ Gutenberg Custom Blocks: Our custom blocks for Gutenberg offer additional functionality and design options to enhance your website building experience. These blocks can be easily inserted into your Gutenberg editor, allowing you to create dynamic and engaging content effortlessly.

    We believe that every website should have access to professional design options, regardless of the user’s technical skills or budget. With WDdesignKit, we aim to provide you with a comprehensive set of templates, widgets, and blocks that make website creation an enjoyable and hassle-free process.
    We are currently in the beta phase, and your feedback is crucial to help us improve and refine WDdesignKit further. We welcome your suggestions, bug reports, and feature requests to make this plugin even better. Together, let’s build stunning WordPress websites with ease!

🏴󠁣󠁯󠁭󠁡󠁧󠁿 Check our other Products

🥇 The Plus Addons for Elementor – Collection of 120+ Powerful Elementor Widgets, 18+ Templates, 300+ UI Blocks and Amazing Listing Builder for Post Types to surprise your clients with amazing Websites.

🥇 The Plus Addons for Gutenberg – Collection of 90+ Powerful Gutenberg Blocks, 10+ Templates, 300+ UI Blocks, Blog Builder, Popup Builder, Header Builder and more to charge up WordPress’s Default Block Builder aka Gutenberg.

🥇 Nexter WordPress Theme – Experience the whole new way of creating stunning WordPress Websites without touching a single line of code using Nexter WordPress them and It’s integrations.
sections.faq:
Will This Work With All Themes ?

Yes this works with all the Theme, but it works best in sync with our Nexter WordPress Theme.

Is Widget Builder free to use?

Yes. Our Elementor Widget Builder, Upcoming Gutenberg Blocks builder and future Builders will be 100% free to use. There are some limitations on the number of widgets you can create in the free plan.

What will existing POSIMYTH Product users receive?

If you have The Plus Addons for Elementor, The Plus Blocks for Gutenberg or Nexter WP Theme, You need to use that key in the activation panel of WDesignKit. That will give you instant access of all Pro Templates and Pro Widgets, (Respective to Plugin you have, If you have The Plus Addons for Elementor, You will get access of all Elementor Related Pro Templates & Widgets). In addition, you will receive additional credits, which you can utilise to store or manage your Templates, Widgets and/or Workspaces on cloud.

When is the exit from the beta phase planned?

We are working on several improvements on background and seeking feedback from public beta users to make it even more feature rich and stable before going live.

Can I save templates from both Elementor Free and Pro using WDesignKit?

Yes, You can save and use Elementor Free and Pro both templates.

sections.reviews:
Best widget builder

By Vishit Shah (vishitshah) on March 20, 2024

I have tried this plugin and love it , it has many innovative features such as you can create custom widgets and also customise pre build widgets too. They have options to build widgets for different editor such as Elementor, Bricks and Gutenburg I have tried one widget for elemetor and it’s work like a charm. Wish luck to team for more future updates.
